Jared C. Tilton/Getty Images (KANSAS CITY, Kan.) â€” The second race in the Sprint Cup Series' Chase "Contender Round" will be staged this weekend.Kansas Speedway will host the Hollywood Casino 400. NBC's coverage of the race will begin at 2:15 p.m. Eastern time.Joey Logano, who won last week at Charlotte and will advance to the next phase of the Chase, tops the standings.Here's a look at the Chase standings:1.
